title: American Horror Story - Season 1 Main Titles
author: TVweb
comment: When I watched the first episode I didn't realize this was the opening until the names started showing up lol
Murder House is my favorite season.
this was the best season of AHS  , storyline and the cast were perfect !
the song is my jam. i have it for my alarm clock.

After watching Scream Queens, I decided to watch Ryan Murphy's other shows because I was very impressed. I came across AHS because of the popularity, and I just finished watching season 1 and I was blown away. Hopefully season 2+3+4+5 will just be as good, I hope the new setting and characters won't ruin the show.
